    public abstract static class Type.StructuralTypeMapping<S>
extends Types.TypeMapping<S>
    A subclass of Types.TypeMapping which applies a mapping recursively to the subterms of a given type expression. This mapping returns the original type is no changes occurred when recursively mapping the original type's subterms.
